{"tid":1291372,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"十萬火急，HKU研究生同我入哂黎","createTime":"2019-07-06T23:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T06:46:35.000Z","uid":136803,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"73008427f737aaff599667b1420176e05c9453bc","tid":1291372,"uid":136803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T23:51:00.000Z","msg":"【學苑專訊】香港大學研究生會（PGSA）將於明日（7月7日）下午兩時於香港大學王賡武講堂舉行週年會員大會（Annual General Meeting）討論修改憲章條文事議，包括：<br />\n<br />\n一．刪除指明須用繁體中文以書寫中文的規定；<br />\n二．強調研究生會作為香港警察註冊社團，所有有關研究生會的活動需要符合基本法；<br />\n三．把修改憲法的門檻要求降低，包括修改憲章的法定會議從週年會員大會（Annual General Meeting）改成普通會員大會（General Meeting），另把修憲的七日通知期改為五日。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣比佢搞一搞，仲叫香港大學咩<br />\n繁體中文同英文都冇埋<br />\n我求下各位聽日翻學校，阻止佢地<br />\n根本on撚9,佢地真係以為自己大哂咁撚樣<br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢個重要過77遊行<br />\n急推<br />\n改左就真係冇咖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f884d292d3a2545d5d9832871a357b9f652183","tid":1291372,"uid":136803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T23:51:37.000Z","msg":"人手推post"},{"pid":"923ab0c661cba696a1dbf8393f04dd0a130e779c","tid":1291372,"uid":136803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T23:51:50.000Z","msg":"人手推post"},{"pid":"70a4c60e8be79174f3d0ca3ebb82dff349878b04","tid":1291372,"uid":136803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T23:52:00.000Z","msg":"人手推post"},{"pid":"e1907f49be3654926fa2dce740fef2ea1810ca37","tid":1291372,"uid":205098,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T23:52:44.000Z","msg":"啲大陸人真係麻鬼煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e680224f111cbe69cdb8c8f71b04e32d03ec5f","tid":1291372,"uid":21038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T23:54:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"